+++ As initially theorized, upon further review it has been discovered that the previously viewed document was the result of data corruption from an unknown source. A revised document has been made available [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/ scp-5039/offset/1|here]]].
[[/div]]
[[/=]]
